### Admin User Management API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7092
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get all users with pagination and search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=&sortBy=1&sortOrder=2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Get users with search by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=john&searchType=1&sortBy=3&sortOrder=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Get users with search by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=@gmail.com&searchType=2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Get users by role
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&roleId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5. Get active users only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Get inactive/banned users only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isActive=false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Create new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "username": "newuser123",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullname": "New User Test",
  "phone": "0123456789",
  "gender": true,
  "dob": "1995-05-15",
  "isactive": true,
  "roleId": 2
}

### 9. Update user information
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "username": "updateduser",
  "fullname": "Updated User Name",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "gender": false,
  "dob": "1990-12-25",
  "isactive": true,
  "roleId": 2
}

### 10. Update user password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "username": "username",
  "fullname": "Full Name",
  "phone": "0123456789",
  "gender": true,
  "dob": "1995-05-15",
  "isactive": true,
  "roleId": 2,
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### 11. Update user status (activate/deactivate)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isactive": false,
  "reason": "Violating community guidelines"
}

### 12. Ban user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1/ban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

"User violated terms of service"

### 13. Unban user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1/unban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14. Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 15. Get all roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Advanced Search Examples

### Search by account ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?searchTerm=123&searchType=4
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Search by phone
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?searchTerm=0123&searchType=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Sort by email ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?sortBy=4&sortOrder=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Sort by creation date descending (newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?sortBy=1&sortOrder=2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Combined filters: Active users with role 2, sorted by username
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?isActive=true&roleId=2&sortBy=3&sortOrder=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Large page size for export
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?pageIndex=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}